ask completion time strictly in format: YYYY-MM-DD HH:mm:ss (for example, 2026-02-25 10:43:00).\n   148вҶ’Don't add extra words or explanations before the date.\n   149вҶ’\n   150вҶ’**Examples:**\n   151вҶ’- `Ready for dev` - 2026-02-11 10:43:00\n   152вҶ’- `Verified` - 2025-12-24 18:15:43\n   153вҶ’\n   154вҶ’### Status Workflow\n   155вҶ’\n   156вҶ’```mermaid\n   157вҶ’flowchart TD\n   158вҶ’\n   159вҶ’A[Ready for Dev]\n   160вҶ’B[Dev in Progress]\n   161вҶ’C[Ready for Review]\n   162вҶ’D[Review in Progress]\n   163вҶ’E[Ready for QA Review]\n   164вҶ’F[QA Review in Progress]\n   165вҶ’G[Verified]\n   166вҶ’H[Blocked]\n   167вҶ’\n   168вҶ’A --> B\n   169вҶ’B --> C\n   170вҶ’C --> D\n   171вҶ’D --> E\n   172вҶ’E --> F\n   173вҶ’F --> G\n   174вҶ’\n   175вҶ’%% Rework loops\n   176вҶ’C -- changes requested --> A\n   177вҶ’F -- bugs found --> A\n   178вҶ’\n   179вҶ’%% Blocked state\n   180вҶ’A -- has unmet dependencies --> H\n   181вҶ’B -- external blocker --> H\n   182вҶ’H -- dependencies resolved --> A\n   183вҶ’H -- blocker removed --> B\n   184вҶ’```\n   185вҶ’\n   186вҶ’### Blocked Status\n   187вҶ’\n   188вҶ’Task enters `Blocked` status when:\n   189вҶ’1. `depends_on` contains a task ID that is not `Verified`\n   190вҶ’2. External blocker exists (no API access, waiting for response, etc.)\n   191вҶ’\n   192вҶ’Task exits `Blocked` status when:\n   193вҶ’1. All tasks in `depends_on` are `Verified`\n   194вҶ’2. External blocker is removed manually via `/unblock_task`\n   195вҶ’\n   196вҶ’---\n   197вҶ’\n   198вҶ’## Dependencies\n   199вҶ’\n   200вҶ’### depends_on\n   201вҶ’\n   202вҶ’Specifies tasks that must complete before this task can start.\n   203вҶ’\n   204вҶ’```yaml\n   205вҶ’depends_on:\n   206вҶ’  - \"CORE-001\"\n   207вҶ’  - \"CORE-002\"\n   208вҶ’```\n   209вҶ’\n   210вҶ’**Rules:**\n   211вҶ’- Task cannot transition from `Ready for dev` to `Dev in progress` if any dependency is not `Verified`\n   212вҶ’- If dependencies are not met, task goes to `Blocked` status\n   213вҶ’- Circular dependencies are not allowed\n   214вҶ’\n   215вҶ’### blocks\n   216вҶ’\n   217вҶ’Specifies tasks that are waiting for this task to complete.\n   218вҶ’\n   219вҶ’```yaml\n   220вҶ’blocks:\n   221вҶ’  - \"CORE-005\"\n   222вҶ’  - \"CORE-006\"\n   223вҶ’```\n   224вҶ’\n   225вҶ’**Rules:**\n   226вҶ’- Automatically populated when another task has this task in its `depends_on`\n   227вҶ’- Used for impact analysis when blocking a task\n   228вҶ’\n   229вҶ’### Dependency Validation\n   230вҶ’\n   231вҶ’Before starting work on a task:\n   232вҶ’1. Check all tasks in `depends_on`\n   233вҶ’2. If any task is not `Verified`:\n   234вҶ’   - Set status to `Blocked`\n   235вҶ’   - Record blocker reason in task\n   236вҶ’3. If all dependencies are `Verified`:\n   237вҶ’   - Allow task to proceed\n   238вҶ’\n   239вҶ’---\n   240вҶ’\n   241вҶ’## Task History (Optional)\n   242вҶ’\n   243вҶ’File `task_history.md` tracks all status changes:\n   244вҶ’\n   245вҶ’```markdown\n   246вҶ’## History\n   247вҶ’\n   248вҶ’| Date | Status | Actor | Comment |\n   249вҶ’|------|--------|-------|---------|\n   250вҶ’| 2026-03-05 10:00 | Ready for dev | User | Task created |\n   251вҶ’| 2026-03-05 10:30 | Dev in progress | senior-android-developer | Started development |\n   252вҶ’| 2026-03-05 14:00 | Ready for review | senior-android-developer | Implementation complete |\n   253вҶ’| 2026-03-05 14:30 | Blocked | android-code-reviewer | Waiting for API docs |\n   254вҶ’| 2026-03-05 15:00 | Ready for review | User | Blocker removed |\n   255вҶ’```\n   256вҶ’\n   257вҶ’---\n   258вҶ’\n   259вҶ’## For Performers\n   260вҶ’\n   261вҶ’### Main Agent\n   262вҶ’Monitors statuses and calls corresponding performers.\n   263вҶ’- `Ready for dev` - calls `android-developer` agent (after checking dependencies)\n   264вҶ’- `Ready for review` - calls `android-code-reviewer` agent\n   265вҶ’- `Ready for QA review` - calls `qa-expert` agent\n   266вҶ’- `Verified` - work finished. Forming response to user\n   267вҶ’- `Blocked` - notify user about blocker\n   268вҶ’\n   269вҶ’**Constraints:**\n   270вҶ’- Main agent is prohibited from setting statuses independently. It can only monitor them and call corresponding agents.\n   271вҶ’- Prohibited from changing task content\n   272вҶ’- Prohibited from moving task to other directories\n   273вҶ’- Must check `depends_on` before allowing task to start\n   274вҶ’\n   275вҶ’### android-developer\n   276вҶ’Only monitors statuses related to development.\n   277вҶ’If status:\n   278вҶ’- `Ready for dev` - Sets new status - `Dev in progress`, because task was picked up.\n   279вҶ’- `Dev in progress` - After completing work, changes to `Ready for review`\n   280вҶ’- `Blocked` (if was in progress) - Record blocker, notify main agent\n   281вҶ’\n   282вҶ’**Requirements:**\n   283вҶ’- Prohibited from changing others' statuses.\n   284вҶ’- Flow strictly `Ready for dev` -> Start work -> Set `Dev in progress` -> Finish work -> Set status `Ready for review`\n   285вҶ’\n   286вҶ’### android-code-reviewer\n   287вҶ’Only monitors statuses related to code review.\n   288вҶ’If status:\n   289вҶ’- `Ready for review` - Sets new status - `Review in Progress`, because task was picked up.\n   290вҶ’- `Review in Progress`\n   291вҶ’  - After completing work, if no comments, changes to `Ready for QA Review`\n   292вҶ’  - After completing work, if there are comments, sets status `Ready for dev`\n   293вҶ’\n   294вҶ’**Requirements:**\n   295вҶ’- Prohibited from changing others' statuses.\n   296вҶ’- Flow strictly `Ready for review` -> Start work -> Set `Review in Progress` -> Finish work -> `Ready for dev` OR `Ready for QA Review`\n   297вҶ’\n   298вҶ’### qa-expert\n   299вҶ’Only monitors statuses related to QA review.\n   300вҶ’If status:\n   301вҶ’- `Ready for QA Review` - Sets new status - `QA Review in Progress`, because task was picked up.\n   302вҶ’- `QA Review in Progress`\n   303вҶ’    - After completing work, if no comments, changes to `Verified`\n   304вҶ’    - After completing work, if there are comments, sets status `Ready for dev`\n   305вҶ’\n   306вҶ’**Requirements:**\n   307вҶ’- Prohibited from changing others' statuses.\n   308вҶ’- Flow strictly `Ready for QA Review` -> Start work -> Set `QA Review in Progress` -> Finish work -> `Ready for dev` OR `Verified`\n   309вҶ’",
