ctory, read `task.md` file\n    92вҶ’3. Parse YAML frontmatter if present, otherwise use legacy parsing\n    93вҶ’4. Apply filters if specified\n    94вҶ’5. Sort by priority (ascending), then by status (ready first), then by ID\n    95вҶ’6. Format and display output\n    96вҶ’\n    97вҶ’### Parsing Task Files\n    98вҶ’\n    99вҶ’**With YAML frontmatter:**\n   100вҶ’```\n   101вҶ’Parse the YAML block between --- markers\n   102вҶ’Extract all fields directly\n   103вҶ’```\n   104вҶ’\n   105вҶ’**Legacy format (no frontmatter):**\n   106вҶ’```\n   107вҶ’ID: Extract from heading (# TASK-ID:)\n   108вҶ’Title: Extract from heading after ID\n   109вҶ’Status: Extract from \"## Status:\" line\n   110вҶ’Priority: Default to 2\n   111вҶ’Type: Default to \"feature\"\n   112вҶ’depends_on: Default to []\n   113вҶ’blocks: Default to []\n   114вҶ’```\n   115вҶ’\n   116вҶ’### Sorting Order\n   117вҶ’\n   118вҶ’1. Priority (1 = Critical first)\n   119вҶ’2. Status order:\n   120вҶ’   - Blocked\n   121вҶ’   - Ready for dev\n   122вҶ’   - Dev in progress\n   123вҶ’   - Ready for review\n   124вҶ’   - Review in progress\n   125вҶ’   - Ready for QA review\n   126вҶ’   - QA review in progress\n   127вҶ’   - Verified\n   128вҶ’3. ID alphabetically\n   129вҶ’\n   130вҶ’## Examples\n   131вҶ’\n   132вҶ’### List all tasks\n   133вҶ’```\n   134вҶ’/list_tasks\n   135вҶ’```\n   136вҶ’\n   137вҶ’### List only ready tasks with high priority\n   138вҶ’```\n   139вҶ’/list_tasks status=ready_for_dev priority=1,2\n   140вҶ’```\n   141вҶ’\n   142вҶ’### List blocked tasks\n   143вҶ’```\n   144вҶ’/list_tasks blocked=true\n   145вҶ’```\n   146вҶ’\n   147вҶ’### List tasks blocking others\n   148вҶ’```\n   149вҶ’/list_tasks blocking=true\n   150вҶ’```\n   151вҶ’\n   152вҶ’### Show tasks that depend on CORE-001\n   153вҶ’```\n   154вҶ’/list_tasks depends_on=CORE-001\n   155вҶ’```\n   156вҶ’\n   157вҶ’### Output as JSON for scripting\n   158вҶ’```\n   159вҶ’/list_tasks format=json\n   160вҶ’```\n   161вҶ’\n   