            "content": "# Task Performer Plugin\n\nStructured development workflow plugin for Claude Code with automated code review and QA verification for mobile applications.\n\n## Overview\n\nTask Performer is a Claude Code plugin that orchestrates a complete development workflow for Android projects. It provides specialized agents and skills to handle:\n\n- **Development** - Implementation of features following best practices\n- **Code Review** - Comprehensive code analysis with actionable feedback\n- **QA Verification** - Build, tests, coverage, security, and accessibility checks\n\n## Installation\n\n### Local Installation\n\n1. Clone or download this repository\n2. Copy the `.claude-plugin` folder to your project root:\n   ```bash\n   cp -r .claude-plugin /path/to/your/project/\n   ```\n3. Copy the `agents` folder:\n   ```bash\n   cp -r agents /path/to/your/project/.claude/\n   ```\n4. Copy the `skills` folder:\n   ```bash\n   cp -r skills /path/to/your/project/.claude/\n   ```\n\n### Directory Structure\n\nAfter installation, your project should have:\n\n```\nyour-project/\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ .claude/\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ agents/\nв”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ senior-android-developer.md\nв”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ android-code-reviewer.md\nв”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ qa-expert.md\nв”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ skills/\nв”Ӯ       в”ңв”Җв”Җ task_management/\nв”Ӯ       в”ңв”Җв”Җ developer_result/\nв”Ӯ       в”ңв”Җв”Җ code_review_result/\nв”Ӯ       в””в”Җв”Җ qa_review_result/\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ .claude-plugin/\nв”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ plugin.json\nв””в”Җв”Җ .claude/\n    в””в”Җв”Җ tasks/\n        в””в”Җв”Җ <TASK-ID>/\n            в”ңв”Җв”Җ task.md\n            в”ңв”Җв”Җ dev_result.md\n            в”ңв”Җв”Җ review_result.md\n            в””в”Җв”Җ qa_review_result.md\n```\n\n## Agents\n\n### senior-android-developer\n\nSenior Android developer agent for:\n- Architecture decisions (MVI, MVVM, Clean Architecture)\n- Kotlin/Java implementation\n- Jetpack Compose UI development\n- Performance optimization\n- Testing strategies\n\n### android-code-reviewer\n\nCode review specialist that analyzes:\n- Architecture compliance\n- Code style and conventions\n- Bug detection (NPE, memory leaks, race conditions)\n- Security vulnerabilities\n\n### qa-expert\n\nQuality assurance agent that verifies:\n- Build status (debug/release)\n- Autotest execution and results\n- Test coverage analysis\n- Security audit (OWASP Mobile Top 10)\n- Accessibility compliance (WCAG 2.1 AA)\n\n## Skills\n\n### task_management\n\nManages task lifecycle and status transitions:\n\n```\nReady for dev вҶ’ Dev in progress вҶ’ Ready for review вҶ’ Review in progress вҶ’ Ready for QA Review вҶ’ QA Review in progress вҶ’ Verified\n```\n\n### developer_result\n\nRecords development work results including:\n- What was done\n- Where changes were made\n- How to verify\n- Tests added\n- Risks and limitations\n\n### code_review_result\n\nRecords code review findings:\n- Architecture assessment\n- Potential bugs\n- Performance issues\n- Security concerns\n- Severity classification\n\n### qa_review_result\n\nRecords QA verification results:\n- Build status\n- Test results and coverage\n- Security audit findings\n- Accessibility compliance\n- Quality score\n\n## Workflow\n\n### 1. Create a Task\n\nCreate a task file at `.claude/tasks/<TASK-ID>/task.md`:\n\n```markdown\n# MUSIC-009\n\n## Title\nAdd progress indicator around track cover\n\n## Problem\nUser doesn't understand how much time remains until end of track.\n\n## Task\nImplement circular progress bar around album cover.\nProgress should update every second.\n\n## Constraints\n- Use Jetpack Compose\n- No third-party libraries\n- Don't degrade performance\n\n## Team\n- senior-android-developer\n- android-code-reviewer\n- qa-expert\n\n## Status\nReady for dev - 2026-01-12 12:15:12\n```\n\n### 2. Run Development\n\nAsk Claude to work on the task:\n```\nWork on task MUSIC-009\n```\n\nThe plugin will:\n1. Assign the task to `senior-android-developer`\n2. Implement the feature\n3. Run code review via `android-code-reviewer`\n4. Run QA verification via `qa-expert`\n5. Update task status through the workflow\n\n### 3. Track Progress\n\nTask status transitions:\n- `Ready for dev` - Waiting for developer\n- `Dev in progress` - Developer working\n- `Ready for review` - Development complete, waiting for review\n- `Review in progress` - Code review in progress\n- `Ready for QA Review` - Review complete, waiting for QA\n- `QA Review in progress` - QA verification in progress\n- `Verified` - All checks passed\n\n## Task Files\n\nEach task generates several files:\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|------|---------|\n| `task.md` | Task description and status |\n| `dev_result.md` | Development results |\n| `review_result.md` | Code review findings |\n| `qa_review_result.md` | QA verification results |\n\n## Examples\n\nExample files are available in the `skills/*/examples/` directories.\n\n## License\n\nMIT License - see [LICENSE](LICENSE) for details.\n\n## Author\n\nMaksim Kosenko\n",
